Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
other.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Imaging
public class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
Represents an appointment with a patient and a provider on a specific date and time. The appointment includes details such as the date, timeslot, patient profile, and provider.
